1. On *želi* da ide u šetnju. (He *wants* to go for a walk.)
2. Kako *želiš* da provedemo vikend? (How do you *want* to spend the weekend?)
3. *Žele* da im se pridružimo na večeri. (They *want* us to join them for dinner.)
4. Oni *žele* da kupe novu kuću. (They *want* to buy a new house.)
5. Ti *želiš* da ti pomognem oko matematike? (Do you *want* me to help you with math?)
6. Moja sestra *želi* da postane doktor. (My sister *wants* to become a doctor.)
7. Oni *žele* da organizuju proslavu za svoju godišnjicu braka. (They *want* to organize a celebration for their wedding anniversary.)
8. Da li *želite* da probate ovaj kolač? (Do you *want* to try this cake?)
9. *Želim* da se zahvalim svima na podršci. (I *want* to thank everyone for their support.)
10. Oni *žele* da otputuju u Egipat. (They *want* to travel to Egypt.)